{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Integrate OUDS","anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","type":"heading"},{"text":"Use Swift Package Manager","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you want to add the iOS library of ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", you need to add our ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"To do that, add a new ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" to your ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" project by refering to it by ","type":"text"},{"code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose whether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds"},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0","type":"text"}]},{"text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0-rc3"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"text":"Import the librairies you need","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" products.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"tip","name":"Tip"},{"code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and useless constants.","type":"text"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Import the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above and all themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes","type":"text"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"level":3,"text":"Chose your theme","type":"heading","anchor":"Chose-your-theme"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" framework provides today four themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Theme","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Compact"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For Sosh products"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Wireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles"}]}]]]},{"level":3,"text":"Apply a theme","type":"heading","anchor":"Apply-a-theme"},{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You will need to use for your application root view the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" also.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"]}],"size":1}]},{"numberOfColumns":2,"type":"row","columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"style":"tip","type":"aside","name":"Tip"},{"anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","text":"Trick for Xcode Preview","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you use Xcode ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit ","type":"text"},{"code":"#Preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"inside the ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Essentials","generated":true,"title":"Essentials","ident